eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.EnergyAssessment
Energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: gross_eya_process (AssessmentProcessDescription): Specification of the model used to calculate the gross EYA estimates. gross_eya_results (list[Result]): Gross energy production predictions in GWh. plant_performance_loss_categories (list[PlantPerformanceCategory]): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. energy_uncertainty_categories (list[EnergyUncertaintyCategory]): Energy related uncertainty assessment categories including results. net_eya_results (list[Result]): Net energy production predictions in GWh, including overall uncertainties and results at different confidence levels.

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: name (str): Name of the wind farm. label (Optional[str]): Abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment. operational_lifetime_start_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime start date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. wind_farm_restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations.
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id_reference (str): The ID of the wind resource assessment on which the turbine wind resource assessment is based. This must refer to an ID of a wind resource assessment included at the top level of the EYA DEF. The schema requires that a turbine wind resource assessment is based on only one wind resource assessment. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. wind_spatial_modelling_processes (list[AssessmentProcessDescription]): Wind spatial modelling processes used in the assessment. wind_speed_results (list[Result]): Final long-term wind speed estimates at the turbine location(s). wind_uncertainty_categories (list[WindUncertaintyCategory]): Wind related uncertainty assessment categories including results.
